Author: blimpopotamus
Text: hey man, if this sub isn’t good for you, that’s ok!  a youtuber i used to follow came out recently and i can’t watch the video because i know it’ll bring me right back to my 2014 suicidal depression.   you’ve moved on from this point in your life. you don’t need to restrict to tolerate your distress, i promise.   do you have other, healthy coping skills? or a support system?  good luck, i believe in you. reach out to me anytime.
